{"activeVersionTag":"latest","latestAvailableVersionTag":"latest","collection":{"info":{"_postman_id":"8669703e-d3c9-48c7-8e49-fa6e88018f88","name":"Simba API","description":"### Welcome to the Pargo API documentation.\n\nFirst make sure you have your login credentials. These credentials can be requested at Pargo. Please visit [https://pargo.co.za](https://pargo.co.za) for more information.\n\nFor the majority of requests a `requestReference` property is send back in the response. You can find this value in the meta property.  \nWhen you encounter any problems, please give us this reference and we’ll be able to lookup this specific request en see what went wrong.\n\nIn this documentation we will use curly brackets `{{` and `}}` to indicate that these values are variables and should be replaces by your real values (without the curly brackets). Eg. when the example looks like this\n\n```\n{\n    \"property\": \"{{abcdef}}\"\n}\n\n ```\n\nYour real request should be like this\n\n```\n{\n    \"property\": \"yourvalue\"\n}\n\n ```","schema":"https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.0.0/collection.json","isPublicCollection":false,"owner":"6593580","collectionId":"8669703e-d3c9-48c7-8e49-fa6e88018f88","publishedId":"Rztso6K1","public":true,"publicUrl":"https://docs.pargo.co.za","privateUrl":"https://go.postman.co/documentation/6593580-8669703e-d3c9-48c7-8e49-fa6e88018f88","customColor":{"top-bar":"FFFFFF","right-sidebar":"303030","highlight":"EF5B25"},"documentationLayout":"classic-double-column","customisation":{"metaTags":[{"name":"description","value":""},{"name":"title","value":""}],"appearance":{"default":"light","themes":[{"name":"dark","logo":null,"colors":{"top-bar":"212121","right-sidebar":"303030","highlight":"FF6C37"}},{"name":"light","logo":null,"colors":{"top-bar":"FFFFFF","right-sidebar":"303030","highlight":"EF5B25"}}]}},"version":"8.10.1","publishDate":"2024-09-17T07:41:28.000Z","activeVersionTag":"latest","documentationTheme":"light","metaTags":{"t